ComicInfo.Title: High Stakes Part 2
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: High Stakes Part 2: Dr. Mindbender is recreating Genghis Khan and schemes to put Snake Eyes into the Brainwave Scanner again to obtain a complete set of his combat moves, unaware that Sean has replaced the original Snake Eyes - and that Laura 343 owes her life to Sean. Dawn suggests they should use the Brainwave Scanner themselves to transfer the original Snake Eyes' memories to Sean. Sean writes a letter to his father which convinces him to become involved.
